message.content:
1. Has Nicole Kidman ever portrayed the character Cersei Lannister in HBO's hit fantasy series Game of Thrones since 2011?
2. Can it be confirmed that Nicole Kidman received three consecutive Emmy Award nominations for Outstanding Supporting Actress in a Drama Series for her performance in Game of Thrones in 2014, 2015, and 2016?
3. Is there credible evidence to support the claim that Nicole Kidman became one of the highest-paid actors on television in 2017 and could earn up to £2 million per episode of Game of Thrones based on shared percentages of syndication payments?
